---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";

const pageTitle = "Privacy Policy";
---

<Layout pageTitle={pageTitle}>
  <div class="content">
    <h2>Privacy Policy</h2>

    <p><strong>Effective Date:</strong> 21/03/2025</p>

    <section>
      <p>
        At <em>Lady Learning</em>, we are committed to protecting your privacy.
        This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and safeguard your
        personal information when you visit our website <em
          >lady-learning.com</em
        > and use our services, including our online English courses. By using our
        website and services, you agree to the collection and use of information
        in accordance with this Privacy Policy.
      </p>
    </section>
    <section>
      <h3>1. Information We Collect</h3>
      <p>
        We collect personal information that you provide to us when you use our
        website or services. This may include:
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li>
          <strong>Personal Identification Information:</strong> Name, email address,
          phone number, and any other details you provide when signing up for courses
          or interacting with our website.
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Payment Information:</strong> If you purchase a course, we may
          collect payment details such as credit card information, but this is processed
          through a secure payment gateway.
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Usage Data:</strong> Information on how you access and use our
          website, including your IP address, browser type, and session duration.
          This helps us improve our website and services.
        </li>
      </ul>
    </section>
    <section>
      <h3>2. How We Use Your Information</h3>
      <p>
        We use your information to provide, personalize, and improve our
        services. Specifically, we may use your information for the following
        purposes:
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li>To create and manage your account and provide course materials.</li>
        <li>To process payments and manage transactions.</li>
        <li>
          To communicate with you about course updates, promotions, or support
          inquiries.
        </li>
        <li>
          To improve our website and services based on user feedback and data.
        </li>
        <li>
          To comply with legal obligations and enforce our terms of service.
        </li>
      </ul>
    </section>
    <section>
      <h3>3. How We Protect Your Information</h3>
      <p>
        We take reasonable steps to protect your personal information from
        unauthorized access, alteration, or disclosure. Our website uses
        encryption and other security technologies to safeguard your data.
      </p>
      <p>
        However, please be aware that no method of transmission over the
        internet or electronic storage is 100% secure, and we cannot guarantee
        absolute security.
      </p>
    </section>
    <section>
      <h3>4. Sharing Your Information</h3>
      <p>
        We do not sell, rent, or share your personal information with third
        parties, except in the following circumstances:
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li>
          <strong>Service Providers:</strong> We may share your information with
          third-party service providers who assist us in running our business, such
          as payment processors, email service providers, and website hosting.
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Legal Requirements:</strong> We may disclose your information if
          required by law or if we believe it’s necessary to protect our rights or
          comply with a legal process.
        </li>
      </ul>
    </section>
    <section>
      <h3>5. Cookies and Tracking Technologies</h3>
      <p>
        We use cookies and similar tracking technologies to enhance your
        experience on our website. These technologies help us remember your
        preferences, analyze trends, and improve our services.
      </p>
      <p>
        You can choose to disable cookies through your browser settings, but
        this may impact your experience on our site.
      </p>
    </section>
    <section>
      <h3>6. Your Rights</h3>
      <p>
        You have the right to access, update, or delete your personal
        information. If you would like to exercise these rights, please contact
        us at [Your Contact Email].
      </p>
      <p>
        If you are located in the European Union (EU), you have additional
        rights under the General Data Protection Regulation (GDPR), including
        the right to withdraw consent, the right to object to data processing,
        and the right to lodge a complaint with a supervisory authority.
      </p>
    </section>
    <section>
      <h3>7. Children’s Privacy</h3>
      <p>
        Our services are not intended for children under the age of 13, and we
        do not knowingly collect personal information from children. If we
        become aware that we have collected personal information from a child
        under 13, we will take steps to delete it.
      </p>
    </section>
    <section>
      <h3>8. Changes to This Privacy Policy</h3>
      <p>
        We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time to reflect changes
        in our practices or legal requirements. We will notify you of any
        significant changes by posting an updated version on this page, along
        with the new effective date.
      </p>
    </section>
    <section>
      <h3>9. Contact Us</h3>
      <p>
        If you have any questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy or how
        we handle your personal information, please contact us at:
      </p>

      <div class="contact">
        <p>Lady Catherine</p>
        <a href="www.lady-catherine.com">www.lady-catherine.com</a>
        <a href="mailto:lady-catherine@mail.com">lady-catherine@mail.com</a>
        <p>01 55 44 99 44</p>
      </div>
    </section>
  </div>
</Layout>

<style scoped>
  @import url("https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:ital,wght@0,100;0,200;0,300;0,400;0,500;0,600;0,700;0,800;0,900;1,100;1,200;1,300;1,400;1,500;1,600;1,700;1,800;1,900&display=swap");

  * {
    font-family: "Lato", sans-serif;
  }

  .content {
    margin: 2rem;
  }

  .contact {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
  }

  .contact > p {
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0;
  }

  h2,
  h3 {
    font-family: "Poppins", sans-serif;
  }

  h2,
  h3,
  .content > p {
    color: #082033;
  }

  @media (width >= 950px) {
    h2,
    h3,
    .content > p {
      text-align: left;
    }
  }
  @media (width < 950px) {
    h2,
    h3,
    .content > p {
      text-align: center;
    }
  }
</style>
